                    Vue.js + Firebase Realtime Database
                    Course Notes


1 - What is Firebase and Why is it so Great
The course shows how to use the realtime Firebase database
  - https://firebase.google.com
  - It is developed with mobile apps in mind
  - It is not however limited to mobile apps
  - There are multiple products available on the platform
  - This course will hwever focus on one, the realtime database
  - When people talk of Firebase they often talk of the whole platform
  

2 - Meet Firebase Realtime Database

3 - Read Data from Firebase with Vue.js

4 - Write Data to Firebase with Vue.js

5 - Delete Data from Firebase with Vue.js

6 - Update Data from Firebase with Vue.js

7 - Update Multiple References at Once

8 - Display Notifications when Things Happen
